eb9ed853-9427-4af8-8a3d-04b68f423298.title: <player>
eb9ed853-9427-4af8-8a3d-04b68f423298.text:
His village is being terrorised by a vampyre! He told me
to ask you about how I can stop it.

e6dd35dd-5730-48dc-956a-180ba4884b99.title: Dr Harlow
e6dd35dd-5730-48dc-956a-180ba4884b99.text:
Buy me a beer... then I'll teash you what you need to
know...

9f54698c-964c-4d04-b022-6e055565de73.title: <player>
9f54698c-964c-4d04-b022-6e055565de73.text: But this is your friend Morgan we're talking about!

e4b503a5-fdfa-4a0f-b790-acbc5ac6bf99.text: You give a beer to Dr Harlow.

9bb0378f-f318-42d5-b425-ab4cd56949ce.title: <player>
9bb0378f-f318-42d5-b425-ab4cd56949ce.text: So tell me how to kill vampyres then.

2bb3465a-bd5d-441e-bf9b-29573183895f.title: Dr Harlow
2bb3465a-bd5d-441e-bf9b-29573183895f.text:
Yesh Yesh vampyres, I was very good at
killing em once...

c28ea1d1-a497-4d76-aa89-2aeb66c06b88.title: Dr Harlow
c28ea1d1-a497-4d76-aa89-2aeb66c06b88.text:
Well, you're going to need a stake, otherwise he'll just
regenerate. Yes, you must have a stake to finish it off...
I just happen to have one with me.

33929a64-de19-4845-b8ab-9fc747303b1b.text: Dr Harlow hands you a stake.

265d0d88-03f8-4682-a473-4e40cb0cf7e3.title: Dr Harlow
265d0d88-03f8-4682-a473-4e40cb0cf7e3.text:
You'll need a hammer as well, to drive it in properly,
your everyday general store hammer will do. One last
thing... It's wise to carry garlic with you, vampyres are
somewhat weakened if they can smell garlic. Morgan

ad39e24b-a468-4ebf-b9c1-1f4114afb296.title: Dr Harlow
ad39e24b-a468-4ebf-b9c1-1f4114afb296.text:
always liked garlic, you should try his house. But
remember, a vampyre is still a dangerous foe!

5613e466-24ab-42a0-85b5-43a9489ba815.title: <player>
5613e466-24ab-42a0-85b5-43a9489ba815.text: I'll just go and buy one.
